=== 《潰逃的迪斯可大象》（2012年 - 至今） ===
[[File:Limp_Bizkit_–_Reload_Festival_2016_36.jpg|thumb]]
2012年2月，林普巴茲提特重返睽違十一年的澳大利亞，參加了{{link-en|聲浪音樂節|Soundwave (Australian music festival)}}<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url = http://themusic.com.au/newsletter/4096/exclusive-limp-bizkit-frontman-shocked-at-bdo-barrier-decision|title = EXCLUSIVE: LIMP BIZKIT FRONTMAN SHOCKED AT BDO BARRIER DECISION|accessdate = 2016-02-05|archive-date = 2012-02-04|archive-url = https://archive.is/20120204075521/http://themusic.com.au/newsletter/4096/exclusive-limp-bizkit-frontman-shocked-at-bdo-barrier-decision|dead-url = no}}</ref>，樂團在每場演出中都會紀念2001年在演出中意外死亡的樂迷{{link-en|潔西卡·米哈利克|Jessica Michalik}}<ref>{{cite news|language = en|title=Limp Bizkit dedicate latest Australian show to BDO tragic|url=http://www.heraldsun.com.au/entertainment/limp-bizkit-dedicate-latest-australian-show-to-bdo-tragic/story-e6frf96f-1226262838878|newspaper={{link-en|Herald Sun|Herald Sun}}|date=2012-02-05}}</ref>。2月24日，林普巴茲提特與{{link-en|現金唱片|Cash Money Records}}簽約，並透露計劃發行一首新單曲〈整裝待發〉、一張錄音室專輯《潰逃的迪斯可大象》和迷你專輯《真的假不了Ⅱ》<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.nme.com/news/limp-bizkit/62487 |title=Limp Bizkit's Fred Durst: 'We're working on the craziest metal record ever' | News |work=新音樂快遞 |date=2012-03-08 |accessdate=2012-04-14 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165454/http://www.nme.com/news/limp-bizkit/62487 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在樂團內部，佛瑞與約翰和致命DJ之間發生衝突，因為約翰和致命DJ使用毒品和酗酒，最後致命DJ退出樂團<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://musicfeeds.com.au/news/limp-bizkits-dj-lethal-ive-been-berated-made-to-look-like-a-drug-addict/ |title=Limp Bizkit’s DJ Lethal: "I’ve Been Berated, Made To Look Like A Drug Addict" - Music News, Reviews, Interviews and Culture |publisher={{link-en|Music Feeds|Music Feeds}} |date=2012-06-01 |accessdate=2012-12-15 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124231635/https://musicfeeds.com.au/news/limp-bizkits-dj-lethal-ive-been-berated-made-to-look-like-a-drug-addict/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

佛瑞與{{link-en|凱文·魯道夫|Kevin Rudolf}}和[[小韋恩|小韋恩]]合作了歌曲〈冠軍〉，成為[[世界摔角娛樂|世界摔角娛樂]]{{link-en|冠軍之夜 (2012年)|Night of Champions (2012)|冠軍之夜}}主題曲。該曲於2012年9月3日在電視轉播活動上首次亮相。這是林普巴茲提特自2003年以來第一次與世界摔角娛樂合作。10月11日，致命DJ在[[推特|推特]]網頁上向樂團道歉，坦承自己喝醉才導致內部衝突<ref>{{cite web|language=en|url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3198013/dj-lethal-reconciles-with-limp-bizkit-is-back-in-the-band|title=DJ Lethal Reconciles With Limp Bizkit: Is Back In The Band|publisher=Bloody Disgusting|date=2012-10-25|accessdate=2017-05-12|archive-date=2017-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170429064734/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3198013/dj-lethal-reconciles-with-limp-bizkit-is-back-in-the-band|dead-url=no}}</ref>。即使他歸隊，但不久後又遭到樂團開除，原因不明<ref>{{cite web| language=en| url=http://www.metalinsider.net/rap-metal-musical-chairs/bizkit-tour-to-be-even-limper-without-dj-lethals-involvement?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed:+MetalInsider+(Metal+Insider)| title=BIZKIT TOUR TO BE EVEN LIMPER WITHOUT DJ LETHAL’S INVOLVEMENT| publisher=Metal Insider| date=2013-03-21| accessdate=2013-04-29| archive-date=2019-05-29| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190529044629/https://www.metalinsider.net/rap-metal-musical-chairs/bizkit-tour-to-be-even-limper-without-dj-lethals-involvement?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed:+MetalInsider+(Metal+Insider)| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年4月16日，發行單曲〈{{link-en|整裝待發 (林普巴茲提特歌曲)|Ready to Go (Limp Bizkit song)|整裝待發}}〉<ref>{{cite web|language = en| url=http://www.amazon.com/dp/B00C7GYQA0/ref=cm_sw_su_dptag=unimotrecunir-20| title= Ready To Go [Explicit]| publisher= [[亞馬遜公司|亞馬遜公司]]| date= 2013-04-16| accessdate= 2013-04-17}}</ref>。11月1日，發行翻唱單曲〈{{link-en|盜賊 (林普巴茲提特歌曲)|Thieves (Ministry song)#Limp Bizkit cover|盜賊}}〉<ref>{{cite web | language=en | url=http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3262731/free-download-limp-bizkit-release-their-cover-of-ministrys-thieves/ | title=[Free Download] Limp Bizkit Release Their Cover Of Ministry's "Thieves" | publisher=Bloody Disgusting | date=2013-11-01 | accessdate=2014-03-20 | last=Barkan | first=Jonathan | archive-date=2014-03-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320173127/http://bloody-disgusting.com/news/3262731/free-download-limp-bizkit-release-their-cover-of-ministrys-thieves/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年8月1日，發行單曲〈{{link-en|無盡殺戮 (林普巴茲提特歌曲)|Endless Slaughter|無盡殺戮}}〉<ref>{{cite web|language = en|url=https://www.facebook.com/limpbizkit/posts/10152149253797548|title=Limp Bizkit - Update - the Endless Slaughter cassettes have been...|publisher= [[Facebook|Facebook]]|date= 2014-06-17| accessdate= 2014-10-15}}</ref>。11月15日，參加[[滑結樂團|滑結樂團]]創辦的{{link-en|滑結音樂節|Knotfest}}，在日本[[幕張展覽館|幕張展覽館]]表演。當天同場的還有[[上帝羔羊樂團|上帝羔羊]]、[[蟑螂老爹|蟑螂老爹]]、[[飛越地平線樂團|飛越地平線]]、[[Coldrain|冷雨]]、{{link-en|琉璃湖畔|Crystal Lake (band)}}等<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://knotfestjapan.com/ |title=KNOTFEST JAPAN 2014 -ノットフェス・ジャパン |publisher=Knotfestjapan.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-11 |archive-date=2014-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140730224721/http://knotfestjapan.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年10月，佛瑞透露樂團已經友好的離開現金唱片，再次成為獨立樂團。他說：「我們真的很喜歡跟小韋恩一起做的音樂，我們喜歡這首歌」<ref>{{cite web|language=en|title=Fred Durst On Limp Bizkit’s Split From Cash Money Records|url=http://www.wdhafm.com/gmi/rocknews/2014/10/01/fred-durst-on-limp-bizkits-split-from-cash-money-records|author=Gary Graff|publisher={{link-en|WDHA-FM|WDHA-FM}}|date=2014-10-01|accessdate=2014-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204041838/http://www.wdhafm.com/gmi/rocknews/2014/10/01/fred-durst-on-limp-bizkits-split-from-cash-money-records|archive-date=2015-02-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。樂團於2015年再度活動，雖然表示新專輯已經在製作的最後階段了，但一直沒有新的消息傳出<ref>{{cite web|language=en|title=2015 YEAR OF THE ELEPHANT - NEW FULL LENGTH ALBUM FROM LIMP BIZKIT "Stampede of the Disco Elephants"|url=https://www.facebook.com/limpbizkit/posts/10152562334047548|author=limpbizkit|publisher=Limp Bizkit|date=2015-01-09|accessdate=2015-01-09|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108104159/https://www.facebook.com/limpbizkit/posts/10152562334047548|dead-url=no}}</ref>。10月，在樂團前往歐洲和[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]巡演之前，貝斯手山姆被診斷患有[[椎間盤|椎間盤]]疾病，由於復雜的神經受壓迫而造成很大的痛苦，這讓他暫時無法與樂團一起演出。山姆表示他將進行手術，接受康復治療<ref>{{cite web|language=en|title=The Real Sam Rivers here...|url=http://www.limpbizkit.org/index.php?showtopic=10605&page=2386#entry1250578|author=Sam Rivers|publisher=www.limpbizkit.org|date=2015-10-26|accessdate=2015-10-26|archive-date=2016-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160101062612/http://www.limpbizkit.org/index.php?showtopic=10605&page=2386#entry1250578|dead-url=no}}</ref>，貝斯位置由{{link-en|塞繆爾·格哈德·邦谷|Samuel Gerhard Mpungu}}支援<ref>{{cite web|language=en|title=En su reemplazo, estará nuevamente el bajista Samuel G. Mpungu, quién ha estado acompañando a la banda durante los últimos shows por Europa!|url=https://www.facebook.com/theboilerweb/photos/a.174541256510.131096.138807011510/10153007424326511/|author=theBoiler.info|publisher=www.facebook.com|date=2015-10-23|accessdate=2015-10-23|archive-date=2016-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205170905/https://www.facebook.com/theboilerweb/photos/a.174541256510.131096.138807011510/10153007424326511/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
